Paul Ready https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paul_Ready 0 Paul Ready is a British actor. He is known principally for his work on stage, but he has also appeared in television, radio and films. He received a commendation at the 2003 Ian Charleson Awards. Paul_Ready is a_British_actor . He is_known principally for his_work on stage , but he has_also_appeared in television_,_radio_and_films .
